overview.en: Through social activities to collect real data on the chain, build a comprehensive financial service platform on the global student chain. Through NLD block chain financial services, more Chinese students can realize their dream of studying abroad, and more overseas students can come to China to experience Chinese culture. Along with the national strategy of One Belt and One Road, it can link up the global students and the global culture. Create the credit finance ecosystem for students.
overview.zh: 通过社交活动采集真实数据上链，打造全球留学生链上综合金融服务平台。通过NLD区块链金融服务，让更多的中国学生实现海外留学的梦想，让更多的海外学生来华感受中华文化。伴随“一带一路”的国家战略，链动全球学生，链动全球文化。打造学生信用金融的通证生态。
